,"body":"Really? I'm glad, I was wondering what I would do if I couldn't find anyone to eat with.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":37,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":37,"voiceId":"event235-02-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Eri","body":"I know, it's a little scary when it's your first time at school.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"event235-02-NPC-003","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Kanako","body":"What should we call you? Your last name Chihaya sounds just like a first name, that's cute. What were you called at your old school?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"event235-02-NPC-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":37}],"windowDisplayName":"Anon","body":"Uh,...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":37,"motionName":"nnf04","expressionName":"smile03","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":37,"voiceId":"event235-02-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":37}],"windowDisplayName":"Anon","body":"... Anon is fine!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":37,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":37,"voiceId":"event235-02-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Kanako","body":"Well then, Anon-chan! You said you were late to enter school because of your family's circumstances, that sounds tough!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"event235-02-NPC-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":37}],"windowDisplayName":"Anon","body":"That's right, it's so hard! Everyone's already formed into friend groups right?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":37,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":37,"voiceId":"event235-02-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Kanako","body":"Huh? But don't you know Tomori-chan? You talked with her this morning.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"event235-02-NPC-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":37}],"windowDisplayName":"Anon","body":"No, no, no! I ran into her picking up some rocks .....","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":37,"motionName":"nnf01","expressionName":"smile03","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":37,"voiceId":"event235-02-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":37}],"windowDisplayName":"Anon","body":"Huh? Wow! What's this? How did feathers land on my desk?.....","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":37,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":37,"voiceId":"event235-02-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":36}],"windowDisplayName":"Tomori","body":"Oh, I'm sorry! I opened my bag and everything flew away....","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":36,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":36,"voiceId":"event235-02-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":37}],"windowDisplayName":"Anon","body":"Oh, are these... Takamatsu-san's?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":37,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":37,"voiceId":"event235-02-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":36}],"windowDisplayName":"Tomori","body":"Tail feathers of a hazel crow... Somewhere there are also the wind-scraped feathers of starlings and pheasants...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":36,"motionName":"sad02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":36,"voiceId":"event235-02-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":37}],"windowDisplayName":"Anon","body":"(Why are there bird feathers in her bag...! And why are there so many of them in there...!?)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":37,"motionName":"nnf03","expressionName":"thinking03","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":37,"voiceId":"event235-02-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Mai","body":"I've never looked at them properly up close, but... feathers are so beautiful when you look at them like this!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"event235-02-NPC-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":36}],"windowDisplayName":"Tomori","body":"! I have many more!\nThey're in the club room, so... please wait...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":36,"motionName":"nnf02","expressionName":"serious01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":36,"voiceId":"event235-02-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Mai","body":"Oh, she's gone...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"event235-02-NPC-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Kanako","body":"I can't believe she collects feathers, she's really cute, isn't she?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"event235-02-NPC-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Eri","body":"Yes, yes. She's more like a squirrel. The other day, she was picking up leaves in the corner of the schoolyard....","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"event235-02-NPC-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":37}],"windowDisplayName":"Anon","body":"(I thought she was an odd little girl... Maybe she's unexpectedly popular...?)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":37,"motionName":"nnf01","expressionName":"thinking03","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":37,"voiceId":"event235-02-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":37}],"windowDisplayName":"Anon","body":"(I mean, she's a beloved character... maybe more like a class mascot.)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":37,"motionName":"nnf04","expressionName":"thinking03","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":37,"voiceId":"event235-02-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":37}],"windowDisplayName":"Anon","body":"... Huh?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":37,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":37,"voiceId":"event235-02-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Mai","body":"What's wrong?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"event235-02-NPC-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":37}],"windowDisplayName":"Anon","body":"I just noticed that a lot of girls in this class brought their instruments.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":37,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":37,"voiceId":"event235-02-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":37}],"windowDisplayName":"Anon","body":"You all brought yours, too. Are you in a band?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":37,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":37,"voiceId":"event235-02-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Mai","body":"We just started, but maybe there are a lot of students in bands at our school.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"event235-02-NPC-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Kanako","body":"I think Tomori-chan is the only one in our class who's not in a band.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"event235-02-NPC-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":37}],"windowDisplayName":"Anon","body":"Wow... everyone is playing in a band...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":37,"motionName":"nnf03","expressionName":"thinking03","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":37,"voiceId":"event235-02-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Eri","body":"How about you, Anon-chan? Do you play any instruments?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"event235-02-NPC-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":37}],"windowDisplayName":"Anon","body":"Heh? Oh, I play a little bit. I guess I'm a guitarist and vocalist...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":37,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":37,"voiceId":"event235-02-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Mai","body":"Wow! Me too, me too! If you like, Anon-chan, why don't you join us in the band? We need another guitarist to play Afterglow songs.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"event235-02-NPC-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":37}],"windowDisplayName":"Anon","body":"(Guitar? If I join this three-piece as a guitarist...)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":37,"motionName":"thinking03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":37,"voiceId":"event235-02-036","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":37}],"windowDisplayName":"Anon","body":"(So that means..... I'll be at the edge...)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":37,"motionName":"sad02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":37,"voiceId":"event235-02-037","